		<div id="tutorial"><h1>Fourple</h1>
		<p>
Joystick Controls: Use the left joystick to move. Hold down the 'A' button, which will let you collect the colored squares. Try to match the walls, by collecting the right colors. Once you've gotten the right color, touch the matching wall, and it will disappear. Then, release the 'A' button to release the squares.</p><p>Once you've removed all the walls, you win!</p>
<p>Mouse controls: Use the mouse to move. Hold down the mouse button, which will let you collect the colored squares. Try to match the walls, by collecting the right colors. Once you've gotten the right color, touch the matching wall, and it will disappear. Then, release the mouse button to release the squares.</p><p>Once you've removed all the walls, you win!</p>
